---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Aerolase Laser Treatment | D-Essence Wellness", "description": "Discover Aerolase laser treatments for acne, rosacea, hyperpigmentation, and skin rejuvenation. Safe, painless, and effective for all skin types with no downtime.", "canonical": "/services/aerolase", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#FFFFFF; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#d9d9d9;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin:1.25rem 0; }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted text-center">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">Aerolase</h1>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-8 h-px w-48 md:w-64 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY: un solo contenedor centrado -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-24">

    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="mx-auto">
      <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
      <section id="description" class="measure mx-auto text-left">
        <p class="text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-900">
          Aerolase is an advanced aesthetic laser treatment designed to safely and non-invasively enhance the health and appearance of the skin. Using its exclusive 650-microsecond technology, the laser penetrates deep into the skin without discomfort or damage to the surface, making it suitable for all skin types and tones. It is highly effective in treating concerns such as acne, scars, dark spots, rosacea, facial veins, fine lines, wrinkles, and other signs of premature aging.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800">
          In addition to targeting these conditions, Aerolase stimulates natural collagen production, resulting in smoother, firmer, and rejuvenated skin. With no downtime required, patients can resume daily activities immediately after treatment, making Aerolase a safe, practical, and comfortable option that delivers natural, long-lasting results.
        </p>

        <ul class="service-attributes mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 md:gap-3" role="list">
          <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1.5 w-1.5"></span>Clearer, healthier skin
          </li>
          <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border rule bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-[11px] md:text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800 shadow-sm">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 h-1.5 w-1.5"></span>Skin rejuvenation
          </li>

        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 text-center">
          “Reveal your best skin—naturally, safely, beautifully.”
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS — diseño pro con tarjetas y halo decorativo -->
<section id="benefits" class="measure mx-auto">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">Benefits</h2>

  <style>
    .benefits-wrap{ position:relative; }
    /* halo de fondo sutil detrás de la grilla */
    .benefits-wrap::before{
      content:""; position:absolute; inset:auto 0 -10% 0; height:220px; 
      background: radial-gradient(60% 60% at 50% 0%,
        rgba(20,20,20,.06), rgba(20,20,20,0) 70%);
      filter: blur(12px);
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .benefit-card{
      position:relative; display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:.9rem;
      padding:1rem 1.1rem; border-radius:1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.92), rgba(255,255,255,.75));
      border:1px solid var(--rule);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(20,20,20,.05);
      transition: transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease, border-color .22s ease;
    }
    .benefit-card:hover{
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(20,20,20,.08);
      border-color:#d9d9d9;
    }
    .benefit-icon{
      width:2.2rem; height:2.2rem; border-radius:999px; position:relative;
      display:grid; place-items:center; flex:0 0 auto;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, rgba(20,20,20,.10), rgba(20,20,20,.03) 60%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1.5px var(--rule), 0 4px 10px rgba(20,20,20,.10);
    }
    .benefit-icon::after{
      content:""; position:absolute; inset:-6px; border-radius:999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 60% 40%, rgba(20,20,20,.06), transparent 60%);
      z-index:-1;
    }
    .benefit-text{ line-height:1.75; color: var(--ink); }
    /* reutilizamos el tamaño del check del sitio pero un pelín mayor en tarjetas */
    .benefit-icon .icon-check{ width:1.2rem; height:1.2rem; margin:0; }
  </style>

  <div class="benefits-wrap mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-5">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <span class="benefit-icon">
        <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <p class="benefit-text">Safe for all skin types.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit-card">
      <span class="benefit-icon">
        <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <p class="benefit-text">Painless, no downtime.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit-card">
      <span class="benefit-icon">
        <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <p class="benefit-text">Targets multiple skin concerns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit-card">
      <span class="benefit-icon">
        <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <p class="benefit-text">Boosts natural collagen.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- THE PROCESS -->
      <section id="process" class="measure mx-auto text-left">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">1</div>
            <p class="tl-title">Consultation</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">Goals, medical history, candidacy, and personalized plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">2</div>
            <p class="tl-title">Treatment</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">Technique and settings tailored to indication and area with comfort in mind.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tl-step">
            <div class="tl-badge">3</div>
            <p class="muted tl-title">Review & Next Steps</p>
            <p class="muted mt-1">What to expect as results evolve; maintenance when helpful.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE / POST — nuevo diseño en tarjetas -->
<section id="care" class="measure mx-auto text-left">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">Pre and Post-Treatment Instructions</h2>

  <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    <!-- Before -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl border rule bg-white/60 shadow-sm p-6">
      <p class="font-medium mb-3">Before your visit</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 muted">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Avoid new actives/irritants if directed.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Disclose medications, allergies, and recent procedures.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Hydrate and arrive with clean skin.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- After -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl border rule bg-white/60 shadow-sm p-6">
      <p class="font-medium mb-3">After your visit</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 muted">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Follow your specific post-care steps.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Protect from heat/sun and pause harsh actives.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Contact us if unexpected reactions occur.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQs — diseño con “orb” decorativo (sin números) -->
<section id="faqs" class="measure mx-auto">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <style>
    /* Tarjeta/animación */
    details.faq-pro summary { list-style: none; cursor: pointer; }
    details.faq-pro summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-card { 
      border-radius: 1rem; 
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(20,20,20,.04);
      transition: background .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, border-color .2s ease;
    }
    details.faq-pro[open] .faq-card {
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(20,20,20,.07);
      border-color: #d9d9d9;
    }
    /* Ornamento en lugar de números */
    .faq-orb{
      width: 2rem; height: 2rem; border-radius: 999px; position: relative;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 40% 35%, rgba(20,20,20,.28), rgba(20,20,20,.05) 60%, transparent 61%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px var(--ink), 0 4px 10px rgba(20,20,20,.15);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }
    .faq-orb::after{
      content:""; position:absolute; inset: 4px; border-radius:999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 60% 65%, rgba(20,20,20,.10), transparent 70%);
    }
    /* Chevron */
    .faq-chevron{ width: 1.15rem; height: 1.15rem; transition: transform .2s ease; flex: 0 0 auto; }
    details.faq-pro[open] .faq-chevron{ transform: rotate(180deg); }
  </style>

  <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
    <!-- Q1 -->
    <details class="faq-pro">
      <summary class="faq-card p-4 md:p-5 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="faq-orb" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <div class="flex-1 text-center font-medium md:text-lg">
          How many sessions will I need?
        </div>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-3 text-center muted">
        <p>It depends on indication, area, and your goals. We outline an initial and maintenance plan during your consultation.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Q2 -->
    <details class="faq-pro">
      <summary class="faq-card p-4 md:p-5 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="faq-orb" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <div class="flex-1 text-center font-medium md:text-lg">
          Will it look natural?
        </div>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-3 text-center muted">
        <p>We favor harmony and restraint for results that feel like you on a good day.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Q3 -->
    <details class="faq-pro">
      <summary class="faq-card p-4 md:p-5 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="faq-orb" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <div class="flex-1 text-center font-medium md:text-lg">
          Is there downtime?
        </div>
        <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-3 text-center muted">
        <p>Most services have minimal downtime; we provide specifics and simple aftercare to follow.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <p class="text-sm muted text-center mt-3">
      *Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>



</BaseLayout>
